'''Nirpi''' (''Mustela nivalis'') lea [[Eurohppá|Eurohpá]] unnimus neahtaealli. Dan guhkkodat lea Sámis 167-227 mm ja deaddu lea 40-130 grámma.

==Earát buoiddat==
Nirppi lagas fuolki lea [[buoidda]], mii lea dušše vehá stuorát go nirpi.
Davvi smávvaealli gohčoduvvo ''Mustela nivalis nivalis''.

